Project Summary
Sauce & Spoon would like to launch a pilot rollout of tabletop menu tablets at the Bar unit of the two of our restaurant locations, North and Downtown.

Project Goals
●	Decrease average table turn time by 30 minutes by end of Q2, resulting in decreased customer wait time.
●	Increase product mix
●	Decrease employee burn out and turn over
●	Reduce the number of negative customer review
●	Cut food waste by 25% by end of March Q2
●	Increase daily guest count by 10% by end of May
●	Increase average check total to $75 by the end of Q2 by selling more appetizer (15%), resulting in increased profit

Deliverables
●	Tablets installation in the bar area of two restaurant location
●	Training plan to train the staff how to use and maintain the newly introduced tablets
●	Clear data points to track metrics 

